text = "Long ago there lived a country. 
A country so fruitful; blossoming trees, lively people, and happiness for all.

But then, as time slowly passed, one company took over: Brain Corp.

They started to control everything, from the people to the ice cream making. 
Everything had now been powered by Brain Corp.

Brain Corp was too powerful for most everyone. . . 
that was until three lucky individuals were granted teleporters. 

Each had been given the specific honor of going back in time to destroy 
specific objects to keep Brain Corp from ever coming to power.

It is now your duty to facilitate them in their journey.

The fate of their universe is now in your hands. . . good luck."
